Rating: 3
Very pretty -- looks like an apple pizza garnished with lovely little sprigs of thyme. An honest flavor -- you can really taste the apples. I think it's nice that the peel stays on; I think that helps contribute to the great apple taste. The thyme is nice but not overpowering. Good with vanilla bean ice cream on the side.

